  "prompt": "I am losing confidence and self esteem. Can anyone help me?",
  "response": "I can offer some supportive advice to help boost your confidence and self-esteem:\n\n1. Practice positive self-talk\n- Challenge negative thoughts\n- Be kind to yourself\n- Use encouraging and supportive language\n\n2. Set small, achievable goals\n- Build confidence through accomplishments\n- Celebrate your progress\n- Break larger goals into smaller steps\n\n3. Take care of yourself\n- Exercise regularly\n- Eat healthy\n- Get enough sleep\n- Practice good personal hygiene\n\n4. Develop new skills\n- Learn something new\n- Take classes or workshops\n- Practice a hobby\n- Build competence and confidence\n\n5. Surround yourself with supportive people\n- Spend time with positive friends\n- Limit interactions with negative people\n- Seek encouragement from loved ones\n\n6. Practice self-compassion\n- Treat yourself with understanding\n- Accept that everyone makes mistakes\n- Focus on personal growth\n\n7. Consider professional help\n- Talk to a therapist\n- Join support groups\n- Seek counseling if needed\n\nWould you like to discuss any of these strategies in more detail or share what might be contributing to your current feelings?",
